sc_catalog.description:
Welcome to the NextGen Talent Gateway Services Catalog! This specialized platform is designed exclusively for graduates and employers engaged with the ServiceNow NextGen Professionals Program. Here, graduates can effortlessly submit and manage their professional profiles, while employers can access a streamlined repository of potential candidates.
Our catalog features a user-friendly interface where graduates can find the 'Graduate Profile Submission' service. This service, powered by our custom Record Producer, allows graduates to input their personal details, ServiceNow skills, certifications, and additional qualifications. The process is intuitive and straightforward, ensuring that your profile showcases your capabilities in the best light.
For employers, this catalog serves as a gateway to discover talented professionals trained in various ServiceNow disciplines. It's an essential tool in your recruitment process, providing access to a diverse pool of skilled individuals ready to contribute to your organization's success.
We've designed this catalog with ease of use and efficiency in mind, ensuring a seamless experience for both graduates and employers. Whether you're looking to kickstart your career or find the perfect candidate for your team, the NextGen Talent Gateway Services Catalog is your go-to resource in the ServiceNow ecosystem.
sc_catalog.title: NextGen Talent Gateway
